{"tid":1476181,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"得返兩日，唔該全部集中推818先啦！","createTime":"2019-08-15T17:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T17:46:16.000Z","uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f77bdeb25a16d40463df727c1fea30ced47a1e50","tid":1476181,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:25:35.000Z","msg":"P牌仔一日一Po只推818一樣！！<br />\n<br />\n而家Facebook同tg都唔覺得有好大力宣傳818<br />\n仲分散咗打緊9月中先截止個個中文課程改革咨詢<br />\n（利申：呢樣野一定要打！但尚有啲時間可以分先後）<br />\n同埋高價向大陸買電個咨詢<br />\n偏偏今日又出埋反對通知書<br />\n令到講參與818嘅聲音更細！<br />\n<br />\n我地要用餘下呢兩日做更多宣傳<br />\n盡量鼓勵身邊嘅和理非唔好怕<br />\n必須要齊心！多人參與！<br />\n要畀<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">信心</span></span>同一份<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">責任感</span>[/size=4]畀大家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個係屬於全民大眾，無分勇武和理非嘅回合</span><br />\n一定要有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過百萬人數</span><br />\n[size=6]<span style=\"color: gold;\">用最和平嘅方式去突顯黑警嘅粗暴同恐怖！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkPKibF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkPKibF.png&h=373c49eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fq5NfYm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFq5NfYm.png&h=b768e00d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3W6gTK1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3W6gTK1.png&h=acc914d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sTMTVYn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsTMTVYn.png&h=be2fdcac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vda5M43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvda5M43.png&h=0dd57a94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJDSr43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJDSr43.png&h=e3b939af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b8300f9af1a2ef0f5258e642f8e98c68e924c